package edu.fiu.jit
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    GenericComponent
    A simple interface showing how to use the Self-check process.
    SelfCheckCapable
    The SelfCheckCapable Interface - creates some basic necessitites for testing - any class that you would like to test can implement this interface and needs to override two simple methods (see below)
